    <p>This project does not implement cookies or tracking technologies, as it is designed solely for educational use.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>No third-party services are used in this project. The project is a stand-alone application developed as part of a course, and it does not involve any external integrations or services.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">5. Data Security</h2>
    <p>As this project is for educational purposes, any data entered is stored locally and is not shared with third parties. Security measures, such as those learned in the course, are applied to protect the integrity of the database and prevent unauthorized access.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>This privacy policy may be updated if additional features are added to the project. Any changes will be noted in future updates.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>

    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:waleed.alisarwar@outlook.com">waleed.alisarwar@outlook.com</a></p>
